<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><h2><strong>CADmeister 2020 Version Upgrade (PRESS)</strong><br> </h2><h3><strong>• DIE-LAYOUT/3DDL •</strong></h3><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_0.1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>1. Set & Edit Various Types of Data for 3DDL　</strong></h4><p>- Management function has been added to control various information settings.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>2. 3DDL Layout Consideration</strong></h4><p>- Transport Considerations function has been added to ExamineLayout command.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>3. Die Structure ASSY Output for 3DDL</strong></h4><p>- Released the functions to output consideration results data into an ASSY structure</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>4. Coordinate System Definition Command Improvement</strong></h4><p>- Added standard axis revolves option in the order of axis revolution.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_4.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>5. “Pierce Automatic Placement” Command for Support Design Changed</strong></h4><p>-  Released an add-on function to detect and compare before & after changing data</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_5.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h3><strong>• PRESS •</strong></h3><h4><strong>6. Product Hole Simplified Measurement for “Pierce Auto Placement” Command</strong></h4><p>- Released an add-on function to support a case where a hole diameter cannot be recognized as PIERCE diameter.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_6.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h3><strong>• FORM-EX •</strong></h3><h4><strong>7.  Global Deformation / Variable Amount Incorporated Deform</strong></h4><p>- Renewed functions of “CAE_Twist” command and “Twist” command have been released.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_7.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>8. “EnterDisplacementFile&Deform” Command</strong></h4><p>- Symmetrical deformation is now enabled through the use of asymmetrical analysis data.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_8.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h3><strong>• Easy_Modeling •</strong></h3><h4><strong>9. “2StepExtendedSurface” Command</strong></h4><p>- Released efficient and user-friendly function to extend surfaces in two stages.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_9.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><h4><strong>10. Ribbon Surface</strong></h4><p>- Released an add-on function to adjust angle of Upper Blade Surface.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/PRESS/CADmeister2020_PRESS_10.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div>